Sign up and fund your account with crypto, credit/debit card, or bank transfer. Browse the Math prediction markets, and when you’re ready you can buy shares in your picks.

### How are markets resolved?
Market resolution relies on trusted or official data sources. For complete clarity, you can check the “Rules” section on any individual market page like “Which company has the best Math AI model end of June?,” to see the exact criteria and sources used to determine the winner.
