| 4  |  ![🇵🇱](https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/svg/1f1f5-1f1f1.svg) Poland  | 5 / 1  | 196  | 3  | 3  | 0  | 0  |  
| **6**  |  ![🇮🇱](https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/17.0.2/svg/1f1ee-1f1f1.svg) Israel  | 6 / 0  | 194  | 4  | 1  | 1  | 0  |  
