## Uncertainties And Gaps

- **Results not yet available:** IMO 2026 takes place July 10–21, 2026. As of the crawl date (June 6, 2026), no results exist. The resolution source page is unpopulated.

- **Perfect score counts for 2016–2021 not confirmed:** The raw research does not provide confirmed perfect score counts for 2016, 2017, 2018, 2019, 2020, or 2021. Gold cutoffs for those years (25, 29, 31, 25, 31, 24) are available but do not directly yield perfect score counts.

- **2022 perfect score count conflict:** The 2025 article states 5 perfect scores in 2025 is "the largest number since 2001," but the Wikipedia source states China's entire 6-member team scored 42/42 in 2022. If 2022 had 6 perfect scores, the 2025 article's claim would be contradicted. This discrepancy is unresolved in the available research.

- **Manifold market distribution not fully scraped:** The specific numerical probability distribution for the Manifold market "How many perfect scores will there be at IMO 2026?" (https://manifold.markets/aidan0626/how-many-perfect-scores-will-there) was not extracted in detail during scrape cycles; only the search snippet was retrieved. The Provider: Manifold section does supply the full distribution (see Market Signals above), but this was not confirmed via direct scrape.

